Virginia Brown Faire https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virginia_Brown_Faire 0 Virginia Brown Faire (born Virginia Labuna, June 26, 1904 – June 30, 1980) was an American silent-film actress, appearing in dramatic films and, later, in sound westerns.
